MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2014-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 12th March, 2014
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 11th March, 2014, Smt. D.
Purandeswari relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State in the Ministry of
Commerce and Industry.
